<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8323941>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Indohya boltoni Harvey & Burger, n. sp., holotype male (WAM T112020): A, carapace, dorsal; B, right pedipalp, dorsal; C, left chela, retrolateral; D, left fixed finger, chelal teeth, retrolateral. Scale lines = 0.5 mm (Fig. B), 0.2 mm (Figs. A, C), 0.1 mm (Fig. D)." ;
