    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Indohya boltoni Harvey & Burger, n. sp.: A, left chela, retrolateral, tritonymph (WAM T137074); B, right chela, retrolateral, deutonymph (WAM T137076); C, left chela, retrolateral, protonymph (WAM T110848). Scale lines = 0.2 mm." ;
